ite Release</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/zh/news/website-release/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:42:34 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/zh/news/website-release/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Wenkai Li (李文凯)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/liwenkai/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/liwenkai/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Yuhao Yang (杨雨豪)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/yangyuhao/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/yangyuhao/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Zhenrong Gu (顾真榕)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/guzhenrong/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/guzhenrong/</guid><description/></item><item><title>团队介绍</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/zh/about/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:49:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/zh/about/</guid><description>我们是一个由张鹏教授领导的研究实验室，专注于网络验证。网络验证是计算机网络领域一个令人兴奋的新方向：它利用形式化方法和仿真/模拟来确保大型复杂计算机网络（如数据中心网络和广域网）的正确性。
自 2015 年以来，我们实验室一直致力于网络验证工作，推出了 VeriDP（CoNEXT'16）。随后，我们提出了数据平面验证器 APKeep（NSDI'20）和 MNV（CoNEXT'23）。目前的研究重点是控制平面验证，初步工作包括 DNA（NSDI'22）、SRE（SIGCOMM'22）和 Expresso（SIGCOMM'24）。其中一些工作已经开源。
We are a research lab led by Prof. Peng Zhang, focusing on Network Verification. Network verfication is an exciting new direction in computer network: it leverages formal methods, together with simulation/emulation to ensure the correctness of large and complex computer networks, e.g., datacenter networks, and wide area networks.
Our lab has been working in network verifiction ever since 2015, with the work of VeriDP (CoNEXT'16).</description></item><item><title>About</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/about/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:45:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/about/</guid><description>We are a research lab of ANTS (Advanced NeTworked Systems group), led by Prof. Peng Zhang. Our lab focuses on the verification, simulation, and emulation of large-scale production computer networks.
Network verification (as well as simulation and emulation) is an exciting direction in computer network, aiming to provide a new toolset for ensuring network reliability. In this direction, we have proposed the data plane verifiers APKeep (NSDI'20) and MNV (CoNEXT'23). The current research focuses is control plane verification, with preliminary work like DNA (NSDI'22), SRE (SIGCOMM'22), and Expresso (SIGCOMM'24).</description></item><item><title>加入我们</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/joinus/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:45:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/joinus/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Yichi Zhang (张亦弛)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/zhangyichi/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Apr 2023 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/zhangyichi/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Wenbing Sun (孙文冰)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/sunwenbing/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Apr 2022 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/sunwenbing/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Zechun Li (李泽春)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/lizechun/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Apr 2022 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/lizechun/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Chongzhi Wang (王崇智)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/wangchongzhi/</link><pubDate>Fri, 30 Apr 2021 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/wangchongzhi/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dan Wang (王丹)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/wangdan/</link><pubDate>Fri, 30 Apr 2021 14:26:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/wangdan/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Ning Kang (康宁)</title><link>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/people/kangning/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2019 14:27:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://xjtu-netverify.github.io/